rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Is board game everyone here playing
lately. Playing games important even
in trying times!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Actually, Kajiji find game in Luxuria
by total coincidence, but it crazy good!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Is game of roll dice on board, buy and
sell real estate, increase own capital,
and make all other player go broke.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Scary part of game is that there no
room for show mercy to opponents,
so competition get quite vicious.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Sometimes even escalate into
traumatic fit or fistfight!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Thanks to game, tensions riding high
in wheelhouse. Sometimes worry if we
able to pilot ship properly in such state.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0008
rows.name:
Whoever come up with this game
is super genius!
